net.hockeyapp.android.metrics

Class MetricsManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hockeyapp.android.metrics.MetricsManager

  • public class MetricsManager
extends java.lang.Object

    Description

    Provides functionality to gather User Metrics, both active users, sessions, and custom events.

      • disableUserMetrics

        public static void disableUserMetrics()
        Disables User Metrics collection and transmission. Use this if your user opts out of telemetry collection.

      • enableUserMetrics

        public static void enableUserMetrics()
        Re-enables User Metrics collection and transmission. Use this if your user granted you telemetry collection. User Metrics collection is enabled by default.
